 you looking for great deals on men’s suits and tuxedos? Macy’s has the best men’s dress clothes on sale and clearance. Check out your favorite brands including, Lauren Ralph Lauren, Tommy Hilfiger, Kenneth Cole Reaction, Bar III and more! What men’s dress clothes do you need? • Men’s Suits. Available in slim to classic fits, you’ll find men’s suits on sale and clearance. From job interviews to special events, a well-tailored suit is a must-have. • Men’s Blazers & Jackets. To keep your style classic, we recommend stocking up on men’s blazers in neutral colors on sale. • Men’s Dress Shirts. We suggest buying a variety of neutral dress shirts that will go with just about any suit or tie. Find great deals on white, light blue and gray dress shirts on sale. If you want a trending look, check out patterned dress shirts like florals, plaid, checks or polka dots. • Men’s Dress Pants. Pair up your dress shirts and jackets with dress pants. Stock up on staple colors on sale like black, gray, khaki and navy for multiple styling options. • Men’s Tuxedos. Are you going to a formal occasion? Look handsome at your next special event in a tuxedo. If you want to stand out from the crowd, we recommend a navy or burgundy tux. • Men’s Accessories. How do you add personality to your suiting look? Add ties and pocket squares in bold colors and patterns. Don’t forget to finish your suit with a tie clip and cufflinks. Want to look sharp and save? Shop men’s suits and tuxedo’s on sale, available at Macy’s. Show more Customer Service Help & FAQs Order Tracking Shipping & Delivery Returns Contact Us Shipping To Go to U.S. site Our Stores Find a Store Tell Us What You Think Macy's Backstage Personal Stylist Macy's Inc. Corporate Sites About Macy's News Room Investors Macy's Gives Be the first to know with our emails If texts are more your style, we can send those too. Sign Me Up Open A Macy's Card & Get 20% Off Open a Macy's Card & Get 20% Off today and tomorrow, * up to a total savings of $1